    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1mesh_1_1Mesh" kindref="compound">Mesh</ref> rendering abstractions and command types. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This namespace provides the core types for mesh rendering. <computeroutput><ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1mesh_1_1MeshRenderable" kindref="compound">MeshRenderable</ref></computeroutput> is a high-level component that can be attached to game objects, combining a shared <computeroutput><ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1RenderPrototype" kindref="compound">RenderPrototype</ref></computeroutput> with optional per-instance <computeroutput>MaterialShaderPropertiesOverride</computeroutput>. <computeroutput><ref refid="classhelios_1_1rendering_1_1mesh_1_1MeshRenderCommand" kindref="compound">MeshRenderCommand</ref></computeroutput> is the low-level command object that encapsulates all data needed for a single mesh draw call. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
